Define: Given I go to the ViewFirstJs example
        NavigateTo /index.html
        WaitForPageTitle "View First Example"

Define: And I type "<TODO_NAME>" into the text box
        ClearAndSendKeys "<TODO_NAME>" to id newTodoText

Define: And I click return
        SendKey Key.RETURN

Define: Then a todo should be added with the name "<TODO_NAME>"
        FindById simple-todo-list
        AssertChildElementsContainText xpath="//tbody//tr" text="<TODO_NAME>"